column5: Anybody fished Halls Lake north of Minden?  What can I expect to catch there?
Smallmouth Bass, I've only caught...nothing of considerable size maybe 2lbs at most.  It's been stocked with Lake Trout as well but never targeted them.
Oh look,it has a toon launch. Need to add to my,toon fishing bucket list.
Fair number of average sized smallies. Lots of cottages on that lake, so fair amount of pressure. Lot of better lakes nearby.
